Great NeighborhoodOutdoor Kitchen872 Jodee Ln, ad date: 10/07/2015 
Great NeighborhoodOutdoor Kitchen872 Jodee Ln, BrookingsThe neighborhood is outstanding and so is this single level home with 3 bdrms, 2 baths, and bonus room that can be used as office space or an additional dining room. Granite kitchen with a bamboo wall and accents. Large windows look out to a private back yard oasis with covered patio, a shop, a finished shed that is used as an art studio. Outdoor kitchen for grilling, a sink, cook-top and a pizza oven for outdoor entertaining. A must see! No. 15459212 $347,000Jude Hodge, Broker RE/MAX Coast & CountryCell: 541-813-9261 Office: 541-412-9535www.OregonCoastLifestyle.com
